data.description: Welcome to this adorably cozy 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home on a level lot tucked on the mountainside. The backyard is fenced for your privacy. The main level common area is quaint with an eat-in kitchen and inviting living room. The bedrooms are comfortably sized, and all on the upper level. The primary bedroom features a sizable linen closet, a walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom. Don't hesitate to snag this home for move-in right away! Selling As-Is!
